  "title": "AB03 - Part-Time Locum Clinic Nurse",
  "description": "<p><strong> Clinic Nurse  (Part time)</strong></p><p>Location: Orchard</p><p>Working days:</p><ul><li>Monday , Tuesday & Thursday (1pm to 5pm) - Mostly </li><li>Wednesday, Friday & Saturday (9am to 1pm)</li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>General duties to support Doctor's work such duties may include assisting the doctor during consults and minor procedures (chaperoning included).</li><li>General cleaning of the equipment and treatment room.</li><li>Attending to patients; including appointment taking, registration, dispensing of drugs (under supervision), addressing simple questions and requests, and providing general service support.</li><li>Ensure smooth clinic operations and accurate documentation using the Plato system.</li></ul><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p>",
